          and innovation also play a key role in addressing global issues and
          achieving sustainable development goals.
        </p>
      </td>
      <td>
        <img
          class="wow animate__animated animate__slideInLeft" style="height: 250px;"
          src="/Images/Benefits of Research.avif"
          alt="AboutUs"
        />
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</section>
